\begin_inset Formula $w_{τ}^{t}=$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\begin{cases}
0.54-0.46cos(\frac{2\text{πt}}{M-1}) & dla\, t=\{\text{τ+0,\,τ+1,\,...,\,τ+M-1}\},\\
0 & w\, przeciwnym\, razie.
\end{cases}\begin{array}{c}
\\
\\
\end{array}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

